Description:
    Produces basic scaffolding for a three.js project

Options:
    RequireJS: Include RequireJS for AMD

Example:
    yo threejs

    This will create:
        Gruntfile.js: Configuration for the task runner.
        bower.json: Front-end packages installed by bower.
        package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

        app/: Your application files.
        test/: Unit tests for your application.

        Make sure all node dependencies are installed and you have installed the grunt-cli (npm install -g grunt-cli).
        Run grunt serve.
